{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-verb}}\n\n# {{lb|fr|figuratively}} to [[give up]]; to stop [[try]]ing\n#* Alors je prends l'instant qui passe\n#* Et prends le temps de le voir qui trace\n#* Sans jamais '''baisser les bras'''\n#* Jamais '''baisser les bras''' (lyrics from [[wikipedia:Tom Frager|Tom Frager]], ''Give Me That Love'')\n\n====Usage notes====\nChiefly used in negative constructions such as {{m|fr||ne baissez pas les bras|don't give up}}.\n\n====Conjugation====\n* see {{m|fr|baisser}}\n\n====See also====\n* {{l|fr|jeter l'éponge}}\n* {{l|fr|lâcher l'affaire}}","alt":[],"syn":[],"type":"verb","forms":[{"mod":"inf","aux":["avoir"],"pronom":false}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/baisser#French\" title=\"baisser\">baisser</a> <a href=\"/wiki/les#French\" title=\"les\">les</a> <a href=\"/wiki/bras#French\" title=\"bras\">bras</a></strong></span>\n</p><ol><li><span class=\"usage-label-sense\"><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content label-content\"><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Glossary#figurative\" title=\"Appendix:Glossary\">figuratively</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac label-brac\">)</span></span> to <a href=\"/wiki/give_up\" title=\"give up\">give up</a>; to stop <a href=\"/wiki/try\" title=\"try\">trying</a>\n<ul><li>Alors je prends l'instant qui passe</li>\n<li>Et prends le temps de le voir qui trace</li>\n<li>Sans jamais <b>baisser les bras</b></li>\n<li>Jamais <b>baisser les bras</b> (lyrics from <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Frager\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Tom Frager\">Tom Frager</a>, <i>Give Me That Love</i>)</li></ul></li></ol><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"Usage_notes\">Usage notes</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=baisser_les_bras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Usage notes\"><span>edit</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-b